":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Panic attack, 可能都有埋anxiety<br />\n睇下臨床心理啦</blockquote><br />\n醫生話係panic attack所引發的間歇性焦慮<br />\n但成日就話唔諗佢就冇事<br />\n我夠知啦 但就係每日都諗今晚點訓<br />\n每晚就係到等眼訓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下其他心理學家啦，精神科淨係開藥架咋<br />\n心理學家會睇下有啲咩trigger到你"},{"pid":"8a110dfb9ce927027424ef566fbe2398ddaee706","tid":386242,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"聽講好似係驚恐症你都似係<br />\n之前睇過醫學雜介紹過"},{"pid":"a3a8f84bed7bb74ac9df735b83c8b6329f06bc55","tid":386242,"uid":130789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人係咪話打個j後會即訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你眼光光果時諗乜？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚你試下作一個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其搵d電影劇情自己作個新既結局/ ff同女神既對話同約會經過，有幾詳細得幾詳細<br />\n通常合埋眼keep住用腦入面想像果邊去ff情景，好快就會進入夢境</blockquote><br />\n攰到乜都諗唔到<br />\n發呆 但就係發呆都訓唔著"},{"pid":"526235c6f776a9e04616d37d145d69e620635bee","tid":386242,"uid":88437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知樓主而家點?情況有無好D?<br />\n有無去搵下心理醫生啊?又或者搵D心理輔導服務?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}